title: What's Going on with Kanye??
itunes:title: What's Going on with Kanye??
description:
Thursday 4/26 - Today on the show after Kanye's twitter rant, we had to open up the phone lines and see what our listeners thought about Kanye's comments about Trump. Also, with all the controversy going on, Charlamagne even decided to give himself "Donkey of the Day" for it. Also, Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
